    <meta property="og:description" content="It is our aim to use this blog as a way to share our experiences of a couple travelling on a budget, and hopefully will help to inspire other fellow adventurers to go out and travel. After all, there is a whole planet out there to explore.It is our aim to use this blog as a way to share our experiences of a couple travelling on a budget, and hopefully will help to inspire other fellow adventurers to go out and travel. After all, there is a whole planet out there to explore." />
